{"name":"Alert on stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Slack in real time","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"minutes","minutesInterval":10}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"e77a5b5f-5591-45df-b2e8-dd80f25c3a2c","name":"Every Few Minutes"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://example-market.com/metrics","options":{"timeout":20000,"response":{"response":{"responseFormat":"text"}}}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[54,400],"id":"9a4ce8b0-f7fb-49bd-9a6f-ada75cd64e64","name":"Fetch Target Page","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"extractHtmlContent","extractionValues":{"values":[{"key":"title","cssSelector":".listing h2","returnValue":"text","returnArray":true},{"key":"price","cssSelector":".listing .price","returnValue":"text","returnArray":true},{"key":"url","cssSelector":".listing a","returnValue":"attribute","attribute":"href","returnArray":true}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.html","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[378,400],"id":"43283345-a9fa-448c-8514-6f13a790a6cf","name":"Extract Listings (CSS)"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Zip parallel arrays into one item per listing\nconst j = $input.first().json;\nconst n = (j.title || []).length;\nconst out = [];\nfor (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n  out.push({ json: { title: j.title[i], price: j.price?.[i], url: j.url?.[i] } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[702,400],"id":"c6b968e9-cc05-42b6-a2ff-6a165dedff16","name":"Rows from Arrays"},{"parameters":{"operation":"read","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1026,910],"id":"afbd7b59-96f6-40ec-812c-ceedcfba6aab","name":"Load Previous Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mergeByFields":{"values":[{"field1":"url","field2":"url"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.compareDatasets","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[1674,400],"id":"c5e4be75-793a-46ec-b8e0-392e0642a426","name":"Diff vs Last Run"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#reporting","cachedResultName":"#reporting"},"text":"=🆕 {{ $json.title }} — {{ $json.price }} ({{ $json.url }})","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[2646,-80],"id":"42c5a775-0105-409b-bc4b-8765f70bf5de","name":"Alert New Findings","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"appendOrUpdate","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":["reportId"],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[2970,460],"id":"579a223e-2f1b-4842-a269-7aebe908e4b5","name":"Update Changed Rows","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[3294,970],"id":"44f3c3b9-a30e-4e3b-bbdb-bec70a491951","name":"Write Fresh Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[3942,400],"id":"2f0eb3fd-e699-466f-b7d6-3780949ff4ce","name":"Merge Diff Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.kpi }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[4914,400],"id":"0038d06a-bb53-4fac-bd81-61896c6fa794","name":"Enrich with Reference Data","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"a9c44197-9d6f-47ea-9731-b49298786cdb","name":"enrichedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"71b0f633-6dd7-410a-85fe-0056c70dd866","name":"enrichmentSource","value":"reference-api","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,400],"id":"28cca409-3a08-4890-b21c-27db7ee62147","name":"Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"operation":"read","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5562,400],"id":"91fc4018-9e1f-412f-baa4-95e88142e4b4","name":"Load Previous Snapshot 2","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\nconst current = $input.first().json;\nconst prev = $('Load Previous Snapshot').first().json || {};\nconst drift = {};\nfor (const k of Object.keys(current)) {\n  if (typeof current[k] === 'number' && typeof prev[k] === 'number' && prev[k] !== 0) {\n    drift[k] = Math.round(((current[k] - prev[k]) / prev[k]) * 1000) / 10;\n  }\n}\nreturn [{ json: { ...current, driftPct: drift, hasDrift: Object.values(drift).some(v => Math.abs(v) > 10) } }];"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[5886,400],"id":"eac6cc21-bc07-430a-b884-1574f48a24d5","name":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"completedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[6210,400],"id":"7c7613d8-373f-48c4-ba72-d35b33f7546f","name":"Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"dataToSave":{"values":[{"key":"runId","value":"={{ $execution.id }}"},{"key":"itemCount","value":"={{ $items().length }}"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.executionData","typeVersion":1,"position":[6534,400],"id":"594657af-1c67-4496-8fe9-01e5aaea2983","name":"Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"df556f2e-1047-41e1-a61b-d57872468a66","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"f7052c51-8440-4b6c-9f04-6a6cf60eba68","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"8e945782-7e0c-452a-9c22-e6a71f6a5424","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6858,400],"id":"b7689238-4f8f-431a-8d98-bb0a5314dbeb","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[7182,400],"id":"dc6b15ab-ea87-4f16-a540-0cfef81f3f15","name":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#reporting","cachedResultName":"#reporting"},"text":"=✅ Alert on stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Slack in real time — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[7506,400],"id":"0b132716-d3d5-4213-ba0a-c27c59d62e42","name":"Send Summary to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"105e519e-2eb8-47f3-a8ca-19c63e637720","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"959db606-5fc6-4b49-a128-dd06f8716b07","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"addc8a2e-763c-45c3-8ba8-683dc9703f11","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6858,1420],"id":"d3c4b71c-7b0e-4311-b28d-c56faa4ee86e","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#reporting","cachedResultName":"#reporting"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[7182,1420],"id":"f0965601-940e-4ad7-9b32-2f32cf95f64e","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[7506,1420],"id":"5d23890b-e433-484d-8322-e10b078cfcde","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Every Few Minutes\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 10 min. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Fetch Target Page","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"d1f3edde-317d-c96d-b70f-531c6cbb11b7","name":"Note: Every Few Minutes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Target Page\n\nGET https://example-market.com/metrics — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Extract Listings (CSS) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"a9fa0187-8980-edd7-5ebc-ab9761b06457","name":"Note: Fetch Target Page"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Extract Listings (CSS)\n\nExtracts structured values from raw HTML via CSS selectors.\n\nNext: Rows from Arrays","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"6f807f9f-b44d-efb8-6737-8597d5e563ce","name":"Note: Extract Listings (CSS)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Rows from Arrays\n\nCustom JavaScript: Zip parallel arrays into one item per listing\n\nNext: Diff vs Last Run","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"d38b043b-4a13-ad25-a05a-84a8c1b29bf4","name":"Note: Rows from Arrays"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff vs Last Run · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,1030],"id":"90e7a4aa-74ce-1f21-fda1-b963587cf8e5","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff vs Last Run\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Alert New Findings · ③→ Update Changed Rows · ④→ Write Fresh Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"b7926dcb-1324-eb4c-4e75-cfbe97dfa68e","name":"Note: Diff vs Last Run"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alert New Findings\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Diff Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,40],"id":"b1542b89-d5f5-be79-8c2e-ae9f99542483","name":"Note: Alert New Findings"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Changed Rows\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Diff Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,580],"id":"bf576499-c7ae-6a5b-bdf3-1921119521f4","name":"Note: Update Changed Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Write Fresh Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Diff Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1090],"id":"d8cef681-0a71-2e7b-e97e-5c64c9d11def","name":"Note: Write Fresh Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Diff Outcomes\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"c94303cd-dd61-751e-7989-505b36bafd5e","name":"Note: Merge Diff Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"7efe8843-e05c-5b19-5751-c6a149ed7162","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot 2","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"da82440e-6e63-1836-755d-2f65565e2c85","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot 2\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"6a959843-227d-88a4-3399-6f908b004a2c","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"0ea1621b-9dc0-6fce-7480-dd727baa8a16","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"27c7194e-9f2d-751e-e6bb-d7eba51e3ffa","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"dbb67c6c-af02-5592-a48a-c4927ebcc43a","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"a443cefb-a213-6a8c-800c-9c92d3a81fcb","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"03f56856-0a75-8236-87be-3f250c3d6280","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"6015b144-4384-f2fd-6bf8-76736282df2f","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,1540],"id":"e9e5edb4-4f66-8142-9e05-f299053385ce","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,1540],"id":"33872232-278e-d5a4-78b3-ec0944deff75","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,1540],"id":"08c75ddf-88bd-be2f-2887-7e7ba8e16836","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Alert on stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Slack in real time\n\n**Pattern:** Threshold Monitoring · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nAlert on stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Slack in real time. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual alerts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nEvery Few Minutes → Fetch Target Page → Extract Listings (CSS) → Rows from Arrays → Diff vs Last Run → Alert New Findings → Merge Diff Outcomes → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to threshold monitoring without manual effort\n- Anyone automating alerts in data\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"2f21a1a3-0e45-39d1-c01b-ee909ff3eea1","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"3754424b-c2d8-4e0b-ee78-88b5ceaf0e5a","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"09aacef4-e4a8-f28e-39de-91fed023db76","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your alerts process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"e0acc7d8-f7e4-344a-6f94-a58d13bcee88","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Every Few Minutes":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Target Page","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Target Page":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Listings (CSS)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"